file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: |
    N32-c Handshake Service.
     Â© 2020, 3GPP Organizational Partners (ARIB, ATIS, CCSA, ETSI, TSDSI, TTA, TTC).
     All rights reserved.
  title: N32 Handshake API
  version: 1.1.0.alpha-3
externalDocs:
  description: 3GPP TS 29.573 V16.2.0; 5G System; Public Land Mobile Network (PLMN)
    Interconnection; Stage 3
  url: http://www.3gpp.org/ftp/Specs/archive/29_series/29.573/
servers:
- url: '{apiRoot}/n32c-handshake/v1'
  variables:
    apiRoot:
      default: https://example.com
      description: apiRoot as defined in clause 4.4 of 3GPP TS 29.501.
paths:
  /exchange-capability:
    post:
      operationId: post_exchange_capability
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/SecNegotiateReqData'
        description: Custom operation for security capability negotiation
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SecNegotiateRspData'
          description: OK (Successful negitiation of security capabilities)
        "400":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad request
        "411":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Length Required
        "413":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Payload Too Large
        "415":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Unsupported Media Type
        "429":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Too Many Requests
        "500":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Internal Server Error
        "503":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Service Unavailable
        default:
          description: Unexpected error
      summary: Security Capability Negotiation
      tags:
      - Security Capability Negotiation
      x-openapi-router-controller: openapi_server.controllers.security_capability_negotiation_controller
  /exchange-params:
    post:
      operationId: post_exchange_params
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/SecParamExchReqData'
        description: Custom operation for parameter exchange
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SecParamExchRspData'
          description: OK (Successful exchange of parameters)
        "400":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad request
        "411":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Length Required
        "413":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Payload Too Large
        "415":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Unsupported Media Type
        "429":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Too Many Requests
        "500":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Internal Server Error
        "503":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Service Unavailable
        default:
          description: Unexpected error
      summary: Parameter Exchange
      tags:
      - Parameter Exchange
      x-openapi-router-controller: openapi_server.controllers.parameter_exchange_controller
  /n32f-error:
    post:
      operationId: post_n32f_error
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/N32fErrorInfo'
        description: Custom operation for n32-f error reporting procedure
        required: true
      responses:
        "204":
          description: successful error reporting
        "400":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad request
        "411":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Length Required
        "413":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Payload Too Large
        "415":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Unsupported Media Type
        "429":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Too Many Requests
        "500":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Internal Server Error
        "503":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Service Unavailable
        default:
          description: Unexpected error
      summary: N32-f Error Reporting Procedure
      tags:
      - N32-f Error Report
      x-openapi-router-controller: openapi_server.controllers.n32_f_error_report_controller
  /n32f-terminate:
    post:
      operationId: post_n32f_terminate
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/N32fContextInfo'
        description: Custom operation for n32-f context termination
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/N32fContextInfo'
          description: OK (Successful exchange of parameters)
        "400":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad request
        "411":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Length Required
        "413":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Payload Too Large
        "415":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Unsupported Media Type
        "429":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Too Many Requests
        "500":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Internal Server Error
        "503":
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Service Unavailable
        default:
          description: Unexpected error
      summary: N32-f Context Terminate
      tags:
      - N32-f Context Terminate
      x-openapi-router-controller: openapi_server.controllers.n32_f_context_terminate_controller
components:
  schemas:
    SecurityCapability:
      anyOf:
      - enum:
        - TLS
        - PRINS
        type: string
      - type: string
    ApiSignature:
      oneOf:
      - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Uri'
      - $ref: '#/components/schemas/CallbackName'
    HttpMethod:
      anyOf:
      - enum:
        - GET
        - PUT
        - POST
        - DELETE
        - PATCH
        - HEAD
        - OPTIONS
        - CONNECT
        - TRACE
        type: string
      - type: string
    IeType:
      anyOf:
      - enum:
        - UEID
        - LOCATION
        - KEY_MATERIAL
        - AUTHENTICATION_MATERIAL
        - AUTHORIZATION_TOKEN
        - OTHER
        - NONSENSITIVE
        type: string
      - type: string
    IeLocation:
      anyOf:
      - enum:
        - URI_PARAM
        - HEADER
        - BODY
        - MULTIPART_BINARY
        type: string
      - type: string
    IeInfo:
      example:
        rspIe: rspIe
        reqIe: reqIe
        isModifiable: true
      properties:
        ieLoc:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/IeLocation'
        ieType:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/IeType'
        reqIe:
          type: string
        rspIe:
          type: string
        isModifiable:
          type: boolean
      required:
      - ieLoc
      - ieType
      type: object
    ApiIeMapping:
      example:
        IeList:
        - rspIe: rspIe
          reqIe: reqIe
          isModifiable: true
        - rspIe: rspIe
          reqIe: reqIe
          isModifiable: true
      properties:
        apiSignature:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ApiSignature'
        apiMethod:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/HttpMethod'
        IeList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/IeInfo'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
      required:
      - IeList
      - apiMethod
      - apiSignature
      type: object
    ProtectionPolicy:
      example:
        apiIeMappingList:
        - IeList:
          - rspIe: rspIe
            reqIe: reqIe
            isModifiable: true
          - rspIe: rspIe
            reqIe: reqIe
            isModifiable: true
        - IeList:
          - rspIe: rspIe
            reqIe: reqIe
            isModifiable: true
          - rspIe: rspIe
            reqIe: reqIe
            isModifiable: true
        dataTypeEncPolicy:
        - null
        - null
      properties:
        apiIeMappingList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ApiIeMapping'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        dataTypeEncPolicy:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/IeType'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
      required:
      - apiIeMappingList
      type: object
    SecNegotiateReqData:
      example:
        sender: sender
        supportedSecCapabilityList:
        - null
        - null
      properties:
        sender:
          description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
          type: string
        supportedSecCapabilityList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/SecurityCapability'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
      required:
      - sender
      - supportedSecCapabilityList
      type: object
    SecNegotiateRspData:
      example:
        sender: sender
      properties:
        sender:
          description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
          type: string
        selectedSecCapability:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/SecurityCapability'
      required:
      - selectedSecCapability
      - sender
      type: object
    SecParamExchReqData:
      example:
        n32fContextId: n32fContextId
        sender: sender
        jwsCipherSuiteList:
        - jwsCipherSuiteList
        - jwsCipherSuiteList
        protectionPolicyInfo:
          apiIeMappingList:
          - IeList:
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
          - IeList:
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
          dataTypeEncPolicy:
          - null
          - null
        jweCipherSuiteList:
        - jweCipherSuiteList
        - jweCipherSuiteList
        ipxProviderSecInfoList:
        - rawPublicKeyList:
          - rawPublicKeyList
          - rawPublicKeyList
          ipxProviderId: ipxProviderId
          certificateList:
          - certificateList
          - certificateList
        - rawPublicKeyList:
          - rawPublicKeyList
          - rawPublicKeyList
          ipxProviderId: ipxProviderId
          certificateList:
          - certificateList
          - certificateList
      properties:
        n32fContextId:
          pattern: ^[A-Fa-f0-9]{16}$
          type: string
        jweCipherSuiteList:
          items:
            type: string
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        jwsCipherSuiteList:
          items:
            type: string
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        protectionPolicyInfo:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProtectionPolicy'
        ipxProviderSecInfoList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/IpxProviderSecInfo'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        sender:
          description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
          type: string
      required:
      - n32fContextId
      type: object
    SecParamExchRspData:
      example:
        n32fContextId: n32fContextId
        selectedJweCipherSuite: selectedJweCipherSuite
        sender: sender
        selProtectionPolicyInfo:
          apiIeMappingList:
          - IeList:
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
          - IeList:
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
            - rspIe: rspIe
              reqIe: reqIe
              isModifiable: true
          dataTypeEncPolicy:
          - null
          - null
        ipxProviderSecInfoList:
        - rawPublicKeyList:
          - rawPublicKeyList
          - rawPublicKeyList
          ipxProviderId: ipxProviderId
          certificateList:
          - certificateList
          - certificateList
        - rawPublicKeyList:
          - rawPublicKeyList
          - rawPublicKeyList
          ipxProviderId: ipxProviderId
          certificateList:
          - certificateList
          - certificateList
        selectedJwsCipherSuite: selectedJwsCipherSuite
      properties:
        n32fContextId:
          pattern: ^[A-Fa-f0-9]{16}$
          type: string
        selectedJweCipherSuite:
          type: string
        selectedJwsCipherSuite:
          type: string
        selProtectionPolicyInfo:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProtectionPolicy'
        ipxProviderSecInfoList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/IpxProviderSecInfo'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        sender:
          description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
          type: string
      required:
      - n32fContextId
      type: object
    N32fContextInfo:
      example:
        n32fContextId: n32fContextId
      properties:
        n32fContextId:
          pattern: ^[A-Fa-f0-9]{16}$
          type: string
      required:
      - n32fContextId
      type: object
    CallbackName:
      properties:
        callbackType:
          type: string
      required:
      - callbackType
      type: object
    N32fErrorInfo:
      example:
        n32fMessageId: n32fMessageId
        errorDetailsList:
        - attribute: attribute
        - attribute: attribute
        failedModificationList:
        - ipxId: ipxId
        - ipxId: ipxId
      properties:
        n32fMessageId:
          type: string
        n32fErrorType:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/N32fErrorType'
        failedModificationList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/FailedModificationInfo'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        errorDetailsList:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/N32fErrorDetail'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
      required:
      - n32fErrorType
      - n32fMessageId
      type: object
    FailedModificationInfo:
      example:
        ipxId: ipxId
      properties:
        ipxId:
          description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
          type: string
        n32fErrorType:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/N32fErrorType'
      required:
      - ipxId
      - n32fErrorType
      type: object
    N32fErrorDetail:
      example:
        attribute: attribute
      properties:
        attribute:
          type: string
        msgReconstructFailReason:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/FailureReason'
      required:
      - attribute
      - msgReconstructFailReason
      type: object
    IpxProviderSecInfo:
      example:
        rawPublicKeyList:
        - rawPublicKeyList
        - rawPublicKeyList
        ipxProviderId: ipxProviderId
        certificateList:
        - certificateList
        - certificateList
      properties:
        ipxProviderId:
          description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
          type: string
        rawPublicKeyList:
          items:
            type: string
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        certificateList:
          items:
            type: string
          minItems: 1
          type: array
      required:
      - ipxProviderId
      type: object
    N32fErrorType:
      anyOf:
      - enum:
        - INTEGRITY_CHECK_FAILED
        - INTEGRITY_CHECK_ON_MODIFICATIONS_FAILED
        - MODIFICATIONS_INSTRUCTIONS_FAILED
        - DECIPHERING_FAILED
        - MESSAGE_RECONSTRUCTION_FAILED
        type: string
      - type: string
    FailureReason:
      anyOf:
      - enum:
        - INVALID_JSON_POINTER
        - INVALID_INDEX_TO_ENCRYPTED_BLOCK
        - INVALID_HTTP_HEADER
        type: string
      - type: string
    ProblemDetails:
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string
        status:
          type: integer
        detail:
          type: string
        instance:
          type: string
        cause:
          type: string
        invalidParams:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/InvalidParam'
          minItems: 1
          type: array
        supportedFeatures:
          pattern: ^[A-Fa-f0-9]*$
          type: string
      type: object
    Uri:
      type: string
    InvalidParam:
      properties:
        param:
          type: string
        reason:
          type: string
      required:
      - param
      type: object
    SupportedFeatures:
      pattern: ^[A-Fa-f0-9]*$
      type: string
    Fqdn:
      description: Fully Qualified Domain Name
      type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/exchange-capability": post: requestBody: contents: application/json: generate schema: field supportedSecCapabilityList: item: anyOf: complex anyOf not implemented
